Subject: rPSA-2007-0019-1 gtk

rPath Security Advisory: 2007-0019-1
Published: 2007-01-25
Products: rPath Linux 1
Rating: Major
Exposure Level Classification:
    Indirect User Deterministic Denial of Service
Updated Versions:
    gtk=/conary.rpath.com@rpl:devel//1/2.8.6-9.7-1

References:
    http://www.cve.mitre.org/cgi-bin/cvename.cgi?name=CVE-2007-0010
    https://issues.rpath.com/browse/RPL-984

Description:
    Previous versions of the gtk package can cause applications using
    gtk image loading to crash when loading malformed GIF files.
